item.title: 2007 South-North Korean Summit
item.description: <img src="http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/upload/news/071003_p01_leaders.jpg" alt=""> South Korean president Rho Moo-hyun and North Korean leader Kim Jeong-il had a historical summit meeting at Pyungyang in North Korea.
